comments: Sabonis (SAC) places his already extended arms against Boucher (TOR) and immediately slides his hands off as marginal body contact occurs in pursuit of the loose ball.
Boucher (TOR) reaches across Sabonis's (SAC) right arm to contest and the contact is marginal before Barnes (TOR) cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) reaches in and dislodges the ball from Siakam (TOR) with his arm and the ensuing arm contact is incidental.
Sabonis (SAC) slightly extends a hand into Boucher's (TOR) back as he releases to reach for the rebound and the contact does not dislodge Boucher from his position.
Sabonis (SAC) jumps to pass and returns to the floor without releasing the ball.
Boucher (TOR) establishes himself in Fox's (SAC) path, firming up and marginal body contact occurs as they disengage.
Sabonis (SAC) extends his right hand into Boucher's (TOR) back, affecting his shot attempt at the rim.
Duarte (SAC) establishes himself in Siakam's (TOR) path and absorbs the marginal contact as they come together during the pick.
Monk (SAC) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Quickley's (TOR) arm after the release.
Boucher (TOR) brushes Fox's (SAC) arm as he gathers the ball and the marginal contact does not affect his SQBR.
Boucher (TOR) cleanly blocks Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) reaches in and initiates contact to Quickley's (TOR) left wrist during his upward shooting motion, affecting his jump shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) briefly grasps Boucher's (TOR) jersey during the pursuit of the rebound and immediately releases it.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in Duarte's (SAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Duarte (SAC) contests Quickley's (TOR) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Murray (SAC).
